org.sql: SELECT SUM(time_entries.hours) AS sum_hours, time_entries.issue_id AS time_entries_issue_id FROM time_entries INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = time_entries.project_id WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'time_tracking') IS NOT NULL AND time_entries.issue_id = "$1" GROUP BY time_entries.issue_id
